commit.message:
Merge pull request #9 from slazav/master

GUI patches

Expand image properly (pack bottomhbox with fill=expand=TRUE).
In the old packing the image did not expand vertically.

Use correct action parameter in save_as dialog.
Use GTK_FILE_CHOOSER_ACTION_SAVE instead of GTK_FILE_CHOOSER_ACTION_OPEN, set default file name to "untitled.txt". With GTK_FILE_CHOOSER_ACTION_OPEN it was not possible to enter new file name with some GTK configurations.

Merge pull request #9 from slazav/master

GUI patches

Expand image properly (pack bottomhbox with fill=expand=TRUE).
In the old packing the image did not expand vertically.

Use correct action parameter in save_as dialog.
Use GTK_FILE_CHOOSER_ACTION_SAVE instead of GTK_FILE_CHOOSER_ACTION_OPEN, set default file name to "untitled.txt". With GTK_FILE_CHOOSER_ACTION_OPEN it was not possible to enter new file name with some GTK configurations.

commit.message: fix argument type warning in gtk_file_chooser_set_current_name
GUI: expand the image properly (pack bottomhbox with fill=expand=TRUE)
GUI: use correct action parameter in save_as dialog
Update README to include how to build from source.
Remove unused variables.
Add a function prototype, and remove one.
Unref G3dataApplication when closing the last window.

Add a key press event handler for the image area.

Added a key press event handler for the image area. When the
scroll window that holds the image has focus, the arrow keys
will scroll the image. However, once the scroll has focus, it
does not relinquish it.
Make windows opened by Open action focused and raised to top.
Set filenames pointer to NULL initially.
Command line options affect program behavior.
Remove some unnecessary headers.
Remove dead code.
Add support for outputting error estimates.
Add support for sorting data on output.
Remove dead code.
Add callback for setting the x or y axis as logarithmic.
Remove InsertImage() function.
Add crosshair cursor when pointer is over image.
Scale image when selected in the File->Open dialog.
Change widget packing.
Remove unnecessary box widgets.
Remove dead code.
Add drag-and-drop.
Add callbacks for the remove buttons.

Update status area with pointer coordinates, if all control
points have been set.
Update status area's nump_entry when new points are added to image.
Draw markers on image when it is clicked on.
Add callback for button_press_event.
